{"tid":2364817,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"南韓新天地教會會長涉嫌妨礙防疫 一審罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-01-13T09:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T10:18:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94064a51d25494a6f4cb111e25772b2ba52a00cf","tid":2364817,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"南韓新天地教會會長李萬熙涉嫌妨礙疫情防控的案件，在水原地方法院一審宣判，法官裁定罪名不成立，但挪用公款和妨礙公務等其他罪名成立，判處有期徒刑3年，緩刑4年。<br />\n<br />\n法院表示，防疫部門要求教會提交設施現狀和教徒名單，是蒐集資料，不能夠視為流行病學調查，因此不能夠因為漏報部分資料，而裁定妨礙防疫。<br />\n<br />\n南韓大邱新天地教會去年爆發疫情，李萬熙涉嫌與教會高層合謀虛報及漏報教徒人數和集會場所、挪用教會資金興建私人官邸，並擅自在公共設施舉行宗教活動，去年8月被捕和起訴，11月獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570207-20210113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570207-20210113.htm&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEZvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=f2cb178e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570207-20210113.htm&h=cc9f6ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570207-20210113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3fc2db5bdc6a8e8df6c351a71358338bf61533b8","tid":2364817,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"韓國總統下場慘啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180406/s00005/32098ad4d91abc8266a2e7719434b6a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180406%2Fs00005%2F32098ad4d91abc8266a2e7719434b6a7.jpg&h=ab9883ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"129ce6a4a8177da7026cdff1e959d533d7f57c48","tid":2364817,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"陳近南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688e6729555d45187eb568a41e3482dee94d26db","tid":2364817,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:48:52.000Z"